Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到新国联人类军的摩尔多瓦基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.72,0:01:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地下400米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深层地壳能抵挡菲斯特姆的读心能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于岛屿的谈话可以作为参考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:01:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参考？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.57,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在这儿会被怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高层人物的实验品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查那种家伙有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.51,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濒临灭绝的日本人知道些什么  要调查清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13话  侵蚀～菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和普通人没有区别吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.03,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是遗传因子确实在融合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是人类吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.69,0:02:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拥有对抗菲斯特姆的力量的新人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.21,0:02:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年前\N菲斯特姆的核所释放的毒素夺走了日本人的生育能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲斯特姆给人类的世界末日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.64,0:02:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了控制灾害扩大\N世界决定连同日本一起消灭核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后幸存的日本人\N偷偷展开了以阿尔比斯为名的阿卡迪尔计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.49,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然失去了生育能力  怎么还能生下孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用人工子宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此研究过程中  孩子们获得了核毒素的免疫力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.58,0:03:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培养了抗衡菲斯特姆的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他们是阿尔比斯的子孙\N可称为是菲斯特姆的天敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.63,0:03:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗传因子操作  FENRIR的地狱清扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应体的无认可使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比斯真是集国际犯罪手段于一身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.90,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生存下去  那些被人类所孤立的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.39,0:03:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也曾经是其中一员吧  巴特兰德博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是互相利用罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.20,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像培养驾驶员一样\N开发能够摧毁菲斯特姆的兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.14,0:04:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑已经走了一星期了  他是不是不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭我们也没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  春日井的父母也离岛了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前是日野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生先生吗  已经不怎么记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.85,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见的父亲也离岛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离200处发现飞行器踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半部正在发送电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.71,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是新国联的鼓动宣传  显示图象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.47,0:04:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由人类军勇敢的后方负责人\N向全世界放送的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.30,0:05:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从2114年第一次遭到菲斯特姆袭击以来30年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.62,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们付出了沉重的代价保护着人类的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.81,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们终于得到了巨大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.98,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  法弗尼尔诺顿模型的勇士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知  敌人能读取我们的思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.73,0:05:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此\N战斗部队越扩大就越容易被敌人看穿战略而受到牵制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.39,0:05:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种机体能够进行单独作战\N抵抗敌人的读心能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以发挥更高的攻防性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类史上最强的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.68,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是我们夺回地球  报仇雪耻的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机体只不过到手一架而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  反正我们这就要去抢一大批了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所欲地用别人的东西  搞什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.13,0:06:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N看了那之后确实会有很多人觉得能战胜菲斯特姆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就清楚了  一骑在人类军那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定正心甘情愿地协助他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算当世界的救世主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.39,0:06:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑正是不愿被人那样看才离开岛屿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能记住上法弗尼尔之前的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.98,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而根本没人听听他的心声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.58,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家尽说些信口开河的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.59,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是五年前在岛上的日野  还记得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日野…伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  你好像见过我儿子了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是被道生先生抓住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  想象得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一上法弗尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在连合作用的影响下就会变得暴躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要把我怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意作为人类军而战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是作为新国联的工作人员为战士们服务呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样比较安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的选择吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.48,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这30年来我们人类的选择极速减少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗  拯救战斗着的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃战斗束手待毙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在岛上没有这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里拼命维护着我们已经忘却的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个巨大的记忆保管箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保存「和平」这一文化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.56,0:08:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日野先生为什么离开岛屿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了战斗着的人制造精良的武器\N这是我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了多打倒一个敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了多拯救一个战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的使命有些变化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变化？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  你愿意到我这儿来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是俘虏啊  能那么做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人类军的参谋总部委员  可以通融一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.13,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到我麾下\N也许可以为你找到战斗之外的出路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之外的出路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好考虑一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么离开了岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.24,0:08:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想知道该为什么而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉无论何处都找不到自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史彦应该为你感到骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之外的出路…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.04,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音刚才去整备库了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.26,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然注意到了精灵号的核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此并非吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非吾等之物便将其在吾等面前处决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等会在此分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等会指引我行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.03,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  吾等亦会指引我行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.93,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个核是很久之前在日本发动的其中一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.91,0:09:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它曾让人类绝望  而现在却是唯一的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等让我赞同你的观点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是理解对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们菲斯特姆想要理解人类而存在于此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没有告诉道弘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方面知道  一方面不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性的分歧才让人类遗留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时却与此相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的个性使我选择了\N不同于道弘也不同于阿卡迪尔计划的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是以你自身的意志赞同我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.57,0:10:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是遵照过去与你同化的真壁红音的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁红音已经不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认这一点  我想让你见见真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会发生新的分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.69,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类和菲斯特姆  双方都未曾体验过的分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算让法弗尼尔做救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是过去  就会立即把它破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.07,0:11:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道弘的领导下  人类军也变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有改变的只有我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.45,0:11:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在一点点前进  没有什么是不会变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里时  有时会无法那么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了太多的过去  好像就这样止步不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.43,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你的研究\N驾驶员的染色体变化被稳定控制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是前进吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.34,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问一骑怎么看待这些设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与菲斯特姆交战数次的他的眼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.73,0:11:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使同化现象积极进化的研究是什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定会说实话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一骑的事被你女儿提点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说「不了解对方的心情就不要信口开河」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去也有人说过同样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有红音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.56,0:12:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说「不了解菲斯特姆的心情可以吗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.33,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了她  我才想把现在的研究继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.95,0:12:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所教会我们的事  对我来说还很遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道是不是应该告诉一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈愿一骑能平安回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了红音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.74,0:12:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是移植了诺顿模型的系统核\N能量就无限增幅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.97,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒尔巴特模型\N是我和道弘所创造的新救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是有没有能驾御它的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是令郎要使用的机体吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经过了脑生长过程的极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后连法弗尼尔也驾驶不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  请在申请书上签字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.82,0:13:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺顿模型  高层的心情不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就好  你就能见到儿子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.84,0:13:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等不准许我与吾等之外的人接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先执行的分歧  已经开始行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等令我以自己的意志理解此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩尔多瓦控制部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.66,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认有多个阿尔海诺特斯型\N正径直朝你方进发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的思考被看穿了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.81,0:14:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下设施内有可能混入了菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该立即离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.58,0:14:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去这里\N凭刚才的演说已经足以激发人类的战意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快撤离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部门准备向菲斯特姆进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.27,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各房门解锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.29,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多架菲斯特姆阿尔海诺特斯型  格兰德尔型出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.62,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔诺顿模型驾驶员请立即赶往34区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.97,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等不让我见真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.09,0:14:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在否定我方的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等没有否定或肯定的概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吾等想勉强恢复宇宙\N却反而将其推向更高次元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.19,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等只是不想给予我更多的分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.17,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后  两人一起看看那核的发展吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等没有发展的概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我现在就来告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.25,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是通向真壁红音所希冀之路的第一道门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能抵挡入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部的防御系统没有启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  到底是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮台10座被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格兰德尔型入侵至第三阶层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪儿都只有战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个岛曾经是乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能去  我就会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.96,0:16:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  动作快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙已经到里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在吗  只有模拟战经验也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.12,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.66,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你能驾驶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.20,0:16:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收来的诺顿模型数据呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.11,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和基地的精锐部队一起已经登上机体了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里会成为真正的决战之地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前只有一件事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.73,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比斯  会把剩下的诺顿模型乖乖交出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.78,0:16:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让他们也参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.73,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要让他们明白\N不在此战斗人类就没有未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.98,0:17:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有实时影象传送过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实时影象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在主显示器上显示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是摩尔多瓦  是新国联的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么传送这样的影象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.42,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回线确认  是从卫星回线传送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星回线？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.25,0:17:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  人类能用的卫星已经没有了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.64,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且看到这样的影象\N全世界人的斗志会受挫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说那正是敌人的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  是菲斯特姆传送这影象…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有先例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是他们特有的情报战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  难道说它们理解了我们的感情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有个有血性的家伙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.96,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑坐在那里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问  那是一骑的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那必须去救他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保证那就是一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城  一骑在那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点  真矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城一定能有什么办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到的  没法派法弗尼尔出击那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没人去就我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在这里袖手旁观太对不起翔子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.93,0:18:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子去了  战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了一骑  为了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不能去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能为了一骑一个人将岛屿置于险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.22,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来最近没好好干过活  闲得发慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让我暂时去散散心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你去哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.48,0:19:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动活动筋骨  去摩尔多瓦附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会许可吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.68,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可是从你的上司那里接受的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你和一骑托付给我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.71,0:19:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫真壁红音的日本GA军第二正式大队\NAS驾驶员大人的亲口命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口  你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  有空的话陪我去一趟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生  不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.10,0:19:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定放弃摩尔多瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按照预定计划执行作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.51,0:19:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.81,0:20:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始进行API-1\N通称龙宫岛及阿尔比斯的占领行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以夺取那岛屿的核为最优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.34,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是那个真壁吗  令人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按计划开始作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要好好发挥作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢  我求你了别去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一定要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是无能为力  所以我能明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.14,0:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去学校  什么也做不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能眼睁睁看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了翔子让我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我只是去把一骑带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的  我答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城也答应我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.42,0:21:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要和一骑好好谈一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.71,0:21:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
